The paper deals with motion planning for legged robots, which is a topic closely related to robotics (cs.RO). The use of Model Predictive Control (MPC) and optimal control algorithms also suggests the paper could belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of parallel processing, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the generation of dynamic gaits, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) or computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
